{"tid":1144934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫委會通過鄧惠瓊方案　3年有限度註冊後免實習","createTime":"2019-05-08T11:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T11:46:16.000Z","uid":126510,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80d16503f34a83031a03f57261f601b6d636c96f","tid":1144934,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:13:17.000Z","msg":"醫委會經過超過5小時討論，投票通過接納由港大教授鄧惠瓊提出的方案，要求海外專科醫生通過執業試，並完成至少3年有限度註冊工作，可以豁免實習期。<br />\n<br />\n有醫委會委員表示，32名委員全部出席今日會議。據了解，會上通過以「明票」及淘汰制方式表決方案，至於上次會議被否決的4個方案，會上沒有討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1456590-20190508.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1456590-20190508.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2FctTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=b19533cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1456590-20190508.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ec2177c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1456590-20190508.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n想問下<br />\n免實習期 係咪都要喺公院度繼續做多幾年？"},{"pid":"e8758739f2c7938506b02b5e4e0db6aec041b38c","tid":1144934,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:37:32.000Z","msg":"主要係cut 左實習期 , 有經驗既海外專科醫生可以直接係指定機構做3年野幫輕下，3年後可留可走"},{"pid":"bf1af1e726a448c46672385dc358b2df349b6b90","tid":1144934,"uid":30830,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:45:11.000Z","msg":"而家衛生署都好似俾<br />\n屌<br />\n最缺人係公立醫院<br />\n叫佢地嚟幫手 on call 先啦唔該"},{"pid":"35da6920a0b9fe8010cdb425175e2b371e9342a6","tid":1144934,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:46:16.000Z","msg":"講到人地好想返黎做咁"}]}